attributes.Long form description: The student begins by disassembling the top table by unscrewing the 8 screws that attach it to the rest of the furniture and leaving them on the table. Finishing disassembling the upper table, the student proceeds to disassemble the middle shelf by unscrewing the 8 screws that hold it to the legs and then the student disassembles the four legs of the furniture to finally finish accommodating the screws and the different pieces on the table. Stacking the shelf on the upper table and joining the legs on the table, thus finalizing the disassembly of the furniture.
